OL,4,CBrook House: High rates of suicide
OL,5,Cattempts at asylum centre
OL,6, High levels of self-harm and suicide
OL,7, attempts have been found among
OL,8, detainees at an immigration centre.
OL,10,FSerious concerns were raised by the
OL,11,FIndependent Monitoring Board (IMB)
OL,12,Fabout Brook House near Gatwick Airport.
OL,14,FThe centre is used to house asylum
OL,15,Fseekers awaiting deportation flights.
OL,17,FSteve Hewer, contract director at
OL,18,FSerco, which runs the centre, said he
OL,19,Fwas pleased the IMB recognised that
OL,20,Fdetainees were "generally treated
OL,21,Fhumanely".
